We are looking for strong candidate with experiences in deep learning and knowledge in edge computing. Successful candidate will work with a speech recognition team and will also be required to develop end-to-end speech recognition system on the edge.
Job Requirements

  Bachelors or Masters in AI, Computer Engineering, Computer Science, Machine Learning
  Proficient in Python/ C++ programming.
  Experience in end-to-end speech AI systems is strongly preferred
  Knowledge on edge computing is preferable.
  Team spirit and problem solving ability
  Excellent verbal and written communication skills
